Broadcom to Announce Provigent Purchase Today, TheMarker Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   W r o b e l
-- 
2011-03-21T09:33:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/broadcom-to-announce-provigent-purchase-today-themarker-says.html
Broadcom Corp. is expected to
announce today its acquisition of Israeli start-up Provigent
Ltd. for as much as $400 million, TheMarker reported today,
without saying where it got the information. A spokesperson for
Provigent was not immediately available to take a call from
Bloomberg.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Wrobel at 
 swrobel4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gwen Ackerman at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net  